snippet.title: FAR Changing Tides Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2021
snippet.description: Check out this trailer revealing gameplay from FAR: Changing Tides, the companion title to 2018's FAR: Lone Sails. FAR: Changing Tides is coming to PC, PlayStation, Xbox and Nintendo Switch in early 2022
